  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to see whether or not the diabetes 1 patients have a neurovascular
      microcirculatory dysfunction using various microvascular tests which have been previously
      validated.

      Microvascular responses will be assessed by Laser Speckle Contrast Imaging and expressed in
      Laser Speckle Perfusion Units (LSPU).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will compare microvascular responses between diabetes type 1 patients with
      matched control-subjects.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
